songs.title: YOUR HAIR
songs.lyrics:
He said
You said beautiful things

I already told you how beautiful your hair is?
Your hair is beautiful

You, you and your hair
Do you think you can share?

I already told you that I love your hair?
I love your hair

I love the way you are

Let's be friends
Friends let's be

I have it
All the time in my head
My dirty head

I already told you how beautiful your hair is?
Your hair is beautiful

You, you and your hair
Do you think you can share?

I already told you that I love your hair?
I love your hair
